611
00:34:24,490 --> 00:34:26,330
and invite your cousin
to the Deer Hunt now.

612
00:34:34,010 --> 00:34:35,530
You're put in a tough spot.

613
00:34:36,530 --> 00:34:37,460
I can understand.

614
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:50,980
Can't you just be

615
00:34:52,740 --> 00:34:53,940
my wife?

616
00:35:04,740 --> 00:35:06,860
(Chijun, Liangya)

617
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:09,340
(Mansion of the Lord of Liangya,
Liangya)

618
00:35:35,380 --> 00:35:37,260
I've already told you.

619
00:35:37,780 --> 00:35:39,170
The Lady

620
00:35:39,690 --> 00:35:41,610
is being favored now,

621
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:43,900
so we can't confront her head-on.

622
00:35:45,210 --> 00:35:47,300
You always say
we should keep a low profile,

623
00:35:47,840 --> 00:35:49,730
but I'm afraid
that might cause future trouble.

624
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:52,340
She whispers in Father's ear every day,

625
00:35:52,780 --> 00:35:54,740
wanting her son Liu Qi
to become the heir.

626
00:35:55,210 --> 00:35:57,170
Do you think
practicing martial arts here

627
00:35:57,170 --> 00:35:58,860
will solve everything?

628
00:35:59,530 --> 00:36:02,260
You need to spend more time
pleasing the Lord.

629
00:36:02,780 --> 00:36:05,010
As long as you win his favor,

630
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:06,820
she can provoke all she wants,

631
00:36:06,980 --> 00:36:08,130
but it won't matter.

632
00:36:08,980 --> 00:36:09,820
Remember:

633
00:36:10,010 --> 00:36:11,260
At the end of the day,

634
00:36:11,340 --> 00:36:12,820
you are the rightful heir.

635
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:15,210
Got it?

636
00:36:34,820 --> 00:36:35,980
I heard

637
00:36:36,420 --> 00:36:38,650
that Wei is about to hold the Deer Hunt.

638
00:36:39,010 --> 00:36:39,940
The invitation

639
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:41,980
has been delivered to the Lord.

640
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:45,570
I believe that if you seize this chance

641
00:36:45,570 --> 00:36:47,170
and make a name for yourself,

642
00:36:47,690 --> 00:36:48,980
your position as the heir

643
00:36:49,380 --> 00:36:51,380
will be secure.

644
00:36:54,210 --> 00:36:55,610
If I go to Wei,

645
00:36:56,170 --> 00:36:58,530
I'm afraid she'll have her way
by father's side.

646
00:37:02,820 --> 00:37:03,860
You have

647
00:37:03,980 --> 00:37:05,530
always been

648
00:37:05,530 --> 00:37:07,010
so indecisive.

649
00:37:09,610 --> 00:37:11,090
I must remind you.

650
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:12,860
Your position right now

651
00:37:12,860 --> 00:37:14,860
is precarious.

652
00:37:21,650 --> 00:37:22,490
Young Master,

653
00:37:25,780 --> 00:37:27,130
the Lord has sent someone

654
00:37:27,130 --> 00:37:27,970
to call for you.

655
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:35,580
Father.

656
00:37:36,780 --> 00:37:37,620
My Lady.

657
00:37:43,170 --> 00:37:44,650
The reason I called you here today

658
00:37:45,130 --> 00:37:47,170
is regarding the Deer Hunt.

659
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:51,380
I've decided to take Qi to Yujun.

660
00:37:59,340 --> 00:38:00,650
Qi is not yet eight years old.

661
00:38:01,010 --> 00:38:01,860
I'm afraid

662
00:38:02,090 --> 00:38:03,820
people will laugh at us

663
00:38:04,090 --> 00:38:05,330
for having a child represent us.

664
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:07,130
Father, please reconsider.

665
00:38:07,740 --> 00:38:09,300
The invitation says

666
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:11,260
they invite the Lord of Liangya
to attend.

667
00:38:12,210 --> 00:38:13,420
With the Lord there,

668
00:38:13,780 --> 00:38:15,650
who'd bully Qi for being young?

669
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:18,170
If there's anything to laugh about,

670
00:38:18,490 --> 00:38:20,860
you lost your engagement

671
00:38:21,050 --> 00:38:23,050
and Panyi to the Lord of Wei

672
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:25,090
and even offended him.

673
00:38:25,690 --> 00:38:27,980
If it weren't
for your repeated mistakes,

674
00:38:28,010 --> 00:38:30,090
why would your father
have to travel at his age

675
00:38:30,090 --> 00:38:31,480
to reconcile with the Lord of Wei?

676
00:38:32,530 --> 00:38:34,420
Why do you insist on going to Yujun

677
00:38:34,610 --> 00:38:36,380
and bring disgrace upon yourself?

678
00:38:37,050 --> 00:38:39,380
I was discussing state affairs
with Father.

679
00:38:39,940 --> 00:38:41,460
How could you, a woman, interrupt?

680
00:38:41,820 --> 00:38:42,860
My Lord...

681
00:38:42,860 --> 00:38:43,760
How impudent!

682
00:38:43,860 --> 00:38:45,530
How dare you defy your mother?

683
00:38:48,010 --> 00:38:49,820
My mother passed away long ago.

684
00:38:50,090 --> 00:38:51,210
My Lord,

685
00:38:51,490 --> 00:38:53,820
Maoqing has never accepted me
as his stepmother

686
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:55,530
and has insulted me repeatedly.

687
00:38:56,740 --> 00:38:58,610
You wicked woman, shut up.

688
00:39:06,610 --> 00:39:08,010
If you defy us again,

689
00:39:08,010 --> 00:39:09,400
I'll deprive you of your position.

690
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:11,490
Leave at once!

691
00:39:18,010 --> 00:39:18,980
Father,

692
00:39:21,050 --> 00:39:22,610
you forced me into this.

693
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:26,690
Guards!

694
00:39:26,780 --> 00:39:27,690
Guards!

695
00:39:38,300 --> 00:39:39,340
Please spare me!

696
00:40:04,170 --> 00:40:05,090
Why?

697
00:40:06,130 --> 00:40:08,050
Why must you commit parricide?

698
00:40:10,940 --> 00:40:13,090
You always think I'm indecisive, right?

699
00:40:14,010 --> 00:40:14,850
What's wrong?

700
00:40:15,940 --> 00:40:17,690
Now, I've become the Lord of Liangya.

701
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:19,900
Aren't you happy about it?

702
00:40:20,050 --> 00:40:22,260
You are the legitimate heir.

703
00:40:22,610 --> 00:40:26,050
Why do you have to bear
the reputation of being unfilial?

704
00:40:26,570 --> 00:40:29,690
Why didn't you consult with me first?

705
00:40:32,860 --> 00:40:35,130
Since you like consultation so much,

706
00:40:36,130 --> 00:40:38,050
