in the future,

707
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:40,530
you can ask my late father.

708
00:40:48,170 --> 00:40:49,860
My uncle is dead now.

709
00:40:51,690 --> 00:40:52,860
The Liu Shan now

710
00:40:53,650 --> 00:40:55,530
