724
00:42:24,768 --> 00:42:28,038
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

725
00:42:28,358 --> 00:42:32,048
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

726
00:42:32,748 --> 00:42:34,678
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

727
00:42:35,218 --> 00:42:40,138
♪How could I ever forget♪

728
00:42:40,718 --> 00:42:42,998
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

729
00:42:42,998 --> 00:42:45,518
♪To spend time with you♪

730
00:42:45,768 --> 00:42:47,128
